<item>
            <title>[HBASE-15936] Sort out how to push to apache/ repositories on Docker Hub</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-15936</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It looks like there&apos;s already a &lt;a href=&quot;https://hub.docker.com/r/apache/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Docker Hub username for Apache stuff&lt;/a&gt;. We should figure out how to use it to push the Docker images we use/build for testing.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
